{{! this.stars is a property defined on the context of the template }}

{{! the purpose of the component below is to render stars depending on the
    rating of the song, which is passed in through songs.hbs. It also enables
    updating the stars that are filled with the onUpdate keyword below. }}

{{#each this.stars as |star|}}
  <button
    type='button'
    {{on 'click' (fn @onUpdate star.rating)}}
    data-test-rr='star-rating-button'
  >
    <FaIcon
      @icon='star'
      @prefix={{if star.full 'fas' 'far'}}
      data-test-rr={{if star.full 'full-star' 'empty-star'}}
    />
  </button>
{{/each}}